'''Norman Reynolds''' ([[March 26]], [[1930s#1934|1934]] &ndash; [[April 6]], [[2023]])<ref name="Obituary" /> was the art director for [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''A New Hope'']],<ref name="ANH" /> and production designer for [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''The Empire Strikes Back'']]<ref name="ESB" /> and [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Return of the Jedi'']].

